@startuml View_Blog_Policy_Sequence_Diagram
title 3.20.3 View Blog & Policy - Sequence Diagram
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
autonumber
autoactivate on

actor "User" as User
boundary "Blog/Policy Page" as Page
control "PublicContentController" as Controller
control "PublicContentService" as Service
entity "PublicContentDAO" as DAO
database "Database" as DB
boundary "public content view" as View

User -> Page: Open blogs or policies
Page -> Controller: GET /blogs or /policies
Controller -> Controller: Determine content type
Controller -> Service: get published content
Service -> DAO: find published content
DAO -> DB: Query published blog or policy
DB --> DAO: Content data
DAO --> Service: Blog or policy list/detail
Service --> Controller: Blog or policy data
Controller -> View: Forward content data
View --> User: Display blog or policy

@enduml
